text: Kellion Knibb (born 25 December 1993) is a Jamaican athlete specialising in the discus throw. She represented her country at the 2016 Summer Olympics without posting a valid throw in the qualification round. She also competed at the 2014 Commonwealth Games finishing sixth. Her personal best in the event is 62.07 metres set in Philadelphia in 2017.
